#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/performance/win_loss.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prorated MRR`: Measures the prorated monthly recurring revenue of "
"an opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MRR proratisé` : mesure le revenu récurrent mensuel proratisé "
