#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/pos_lna.rst:7
msgid ""
"`Local Network Access <https://developer.chrome.com/release-notes/"
"142#local_network_access_restrictions>`_ is a security feature that limits a "
"website's ability to send requests to servers on a local network. Access "
"requires explicit user permission, which makes it possible to grant network "
"access to a specific web page. Using |LNA|, Odoo Point of Sale can "
"communicate with devices with local access, such as :ref:`supported ePOS "
"printers <pos/epos-printers/supported-printers>`, directly from the browser "
"and without requiring an :doc:`SSL certificate <epos_ssc>`."
msgstr ""
"`Local Network Access <https://developer.chrome.com/release-notes/"
"142#local_network_access_restrictions>`_ est une fonctionnalité de sécurité "
"qui limite la capacité d'un site web à envoyer des requêtes vers des "
"serveurs sur un réseau local. L'accès nécessite une autorisation explicite "
"de l'utilisateur, ce qui permet d'accorder l'accès réseau à une page web "
"spécifique. En utilisant |LNA|, Odoo Point de Vente peut communiquer avec "
"des appareils à accès local, tels que les :ref:`imprimantes ePOS compatibles "
"<pos/epos-printers/supported-printers>`, directement depuis le navigateur et "
"sans nécessiter de :doc:`certificat SSL <epos_ssc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/pos_lna.rst:15
msgid ""
"Local Network Access is available in most browsers based on `Chromium "
"version 142 <https://developer.chrome.com/release-notes/142>`_ or higher, "
"including Google Chrome, Brave, Microsoft Edge, Vivaldi, and Opera."
msgstr ""
"L'accès réseau local est disponible dans la plupart des navigateurs basés "
"sur `Chromium version 142 <https://developer.chrome.com/release-notes/142>`_ "
"ou supérieure, incluant Google Chrome, Brave, Microsoft Edge, Vivaldi et "
"Opera."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/pos_lna.rst:20
