#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank App (QR Code)`: Add at least one :ref:`bank account "
"<accounting/journals/bank>` to the journal to enable :doc:`QR code payments "
"<payment_methods/qr_code_payment>` with a bank app. Select a :guilabel:`QR "
