"application bancaire. Sélectionner un :guilabel:`format de code QR` dans le "
"formulaire."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cash Machine`: Connect a :doc:`Cashdro <payment_methods/"
"cash_machines/cashdro>` or a :doc:`Glory <payment_methods/cash_machines/"
"glory>` :doc:`cash machine <payment_methods/cash_machines>` to automate the "
"point of sale's cash transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cash Machine` : connecter une :doc:`Cashdro <payment_methods/"
"cash_machines/cashdro>` ou une :doc:`Glory <payment_methods/cash_machines/"
"glory>` :doc:`caisse automatique <payment_methods/cash_machines>` pour "
"automatiser les transactions en espèces du point de vente."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods.rst:67
