msgstr ""
"Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Paramètres Cashdro`, saisir l'adresse IP de la "
"machine Cashdro dans le champ :guilabel:`IP Cashdro`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:65
msgid ""
"Enter your Cashdro user credentials in the :guilabel:`Cashdro Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Cashdro Password` fields."
msgstr ""
"Saisir vos identifiants utilisateur Cashdro dans les champs :guilabel:`Nom "
"d'utilisateur Cashdro` et :guilabel:`Mot de passe Cashdro`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:67
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Cashdro Local Network Access`."
msgstr "Activer :guilabel:`Accès réseau local Cashdro`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:70
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to use :doc:`Local Network Access <../../"
"hardware_network/pos_lna>`, as it bypasses the need for an :doc:`SSL "
"certificate <../../hardware_network/epos_ssc>`."
msgstr ""
"Il est fortement recommandé d'utiliser :doc:`l'accès réseau local <../../"
"hardware_network/pos_lna>`, car cela évite le besoin d'un :doc:`certificat "
"SSL <../../hardware_network/epos_ssc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:74
