msgstr ":doc:`../../payment_methods`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:3
msgid "Cashmatic"
msgstr "Cashmatic"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Cashmatic <https://cashmatic.eu/>`_ :doc:`cash machines <../cash_machines>` "
"automate cash transactions by accepting cash and dispensing change. When "
"integrated with Odoo Point of Sale, payments are processed directly through "
"the machine from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-register>`."
msgstr ""
"Les :doc:`machines de caisse <../cash_machines>` `Cashmatic <https://"
"cashmatic.eu/>`_ automatisent les transactions en espèces en acceptant les "
"espèces et en rendant la monnaie. Lorsqu'elles sont intégrées avec le Point "
"de Vente Odoo, les paiements sont traités directement via la machine depuis "
"le :ref:`terminal Point de Vente <pos/use/open-register>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:11
msgid ""
"The integration with the Cashmatic cash machine only supports payments and "
"refunds."
msgstr ""
"L'intégration avec la machine de caisse Cashmatic ne prend en charge que les "
"paiements et les remboursements."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:12
msgid ""
"Tasks such as filling and emptying the machine must be performed directly "
"through the cash machine interface or via the MyCashmatic app (available on "
"`Android <https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?"
"id=com.cashmatic.app&pcampaignid=web_share>`_ or `iOS <https://"
"apps.apple.com/us/app/mycashmatic/id1661294811>`_) or `website <https://"
"cashmatic.be/my-cashmatic/login>`_."
msgstr ""
"Les tâches telles que le remplissage et la vidange de la machine doivent "
"être effectuées directement via l'interface de la machine de caisse ou via "
"l'application MyCashmatic (disponible sur `Android <https://play.google.com/"
"store/apps/details?id=com.cashmatic.app&pcampaignid=web_share>`_ ou `iOS "
"<https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mycashmatic/id1661294811>`_) ou le `site web "
"<https://cashmatic.be/my-cashmatic/login>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:24
msgid ""
"Two separate sets of credentials are provided with the machine: one for the "
"cash machine, required to :ref:`configure it in Odoo <pos/cashmatic/"
"odoo_configuration>`, and one for the **MyCashmatic** app or website, "
"required to configure the cash machine itself."
msgstr ""
"Deux ensembles distincts d'identifiants sont fournis avec la machine : un "
"pour la machine de caisse, requis pour la :ref:`configurer dans Odoo <pos/"
"cashmatic/odoo_configuration>`, et un pour l'application ou le site web "
"**MyCashmatic**, requis pour configurer la machine de caisse elle-même."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:27
msgid ""
"The Cashmatic machine must be on the same local network as the device "
"running Odoo Point of Sale and must be assigned a static IP address to "
"ensure stable operation."
msgstr ""
"La machine Cashmatic doit se trouver sur le même réseau local que l'appareil "
"exécutant le Point de Vente Odoo et doit se voir attribuer une adresse IP "
"statique pour garantir un fonctionnement stable."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:29
msgid ""
"Setting up the Cashmatic machine requires the hardware administrator's "
"password and technical knowledge. Contact your Cashmatic integration partner "
"for configuration support if assistance is needed."
msgstr ""
"La configuration de la machine Cashmatic nécessite le mot de passe de "
"l'administrateur matériel et des connaissances techniques. Contactez votre "
"partenaire d'intégration Cashmatic pour obtenir une assistance à la "
"configuration si nécessaire."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:33
msgid ""
"Configuring the Cashmatic machine as a :ref:`payment method in Odoo <pos/"
"cashmatic/odoo_configuration>` requires locating the machine's :ref:`IP "
"address <pos/cashmatic/ip-address>` and preparing for connection "
"over :ref:`HTTPS <pos/cashmatic/https>` or :ref:`HTTP <pos/cashmatic/http>`."
msgstr ""
"Configurer la machine Cashmatic comme :ref:`méthode de paiement dans Odoo "
"<pos/cashmatic/odoo_configuration>` nécessite de localiser l':ref:`adresse "
"IP <pos/cashmatic/ip-address>` de la machine et de préparer la connexion via "
":ref:`HTTPS <pos/cashmatic/https>` ou :ref:`HTTP <pos/cashmatic/http>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:39
msgid ""
"HTTPS provides a more secure connection and requires additional "
"configuration, including installing a valid certificate. HTTP allows "
"communication through :doc:`../../hardware_network/pos_lna` and is "
"recommended as it is simpler to set up."
msgstr ""
"HTTPS offre une connexion plus sécurisée et nécessite une configuration "
"supplémentaire, incluant l'installation d'un certificat valide. HTTP permet "
"la communication via :doc:`../../hardware_network/pos_lna` et est recommandé "
"car il est plus simple à configurer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:46
msgid "Locate the IP address"
msgstr "Localiser l'adresse IP"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:48
msgid "To locate the Cashmatic IP address, use one of the following methods:"
msgstr ""
"Pour localiser l'adresse IP Cashmatic, utiliser l'une des méthodes suivantes "
":"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:50
msgid ""
"On the Cashmatic machine, log in with the provided credentials, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> IP address`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la machine Cashmatic, se connecter avec les identifiants fournis, puis "
"aller dans :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Adresse IP`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:52
msgid ""
"In the MyCashmatic app or on the website, sign in to your account, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Network`."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'application MyCashmatic ou sur le site web, se connecter à votre "
"compte, puis aller dans :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Réseau`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:55
msgid ""
"Note the IP address displayed on the machine's or the device's screen, as it "
"is needed for the :ref:`Odoo configuration step <pos/cashmatic/"
"odoo_configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Noter l'adresse IP affichée sur l'écran de la machine ou de l'appareil, car "
"elle est nécessaire pour l':ref:`étape de configuration Odoo <pos/cashmatic/"
"odoo_configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:61
msgid "Connection over HTTPS"
msgstr "Connexion via HTTPS"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:63
msgid ""
"To connect the Cashmatic machine over HTTPS, a valid certificate is "
"required. To generate and download the certificate, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pour connecter la machine Cashmatic via HTTPS, un certificat valide est "
"requis. Pour générer et télécharger le certificat, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:66
msgid ""
"Open a web browser and type the IP address in the address bar to access the "
"Cashmatic web interface."
msgstr ""
"Ouvrir un navigateur web et saisir l'adresse IP dans la barre d'adresse pour "
"accéder à l'interface web Cashmatic."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the interface's side menu, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Device`."
msgstr ""
"Dans le menu latéral de l'interface, aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> "
"Appareil`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:69
msgid "Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Use Cashmatic CA` option and enable it."
msgstr ""
"Faire défiler jusqu'à l'option :guilabel:`Utiliser Cashmatic CA` et "
"l'activer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:70
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Save` and refresh the page. A :guilabel:`Download HTTPS "
"Certificate` link appears at the bottom left of the side menu."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer` et actualiser la page. Un lien "
":guilabel:`Télécharger le certificat HTTPS` apparaît en bas à gauche du menu "
"latéral."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:72
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`Download HTTPS Certificate` link."
msgstr "Cliquer sur le lien :guilabel:`Télécharger le certificat HTTPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:74
msgid ""
"To install the certificate on the device running Odoo Point of Sale, contact "
"your integration partner, as the process depends on the device's operating "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Pour installer le certificat sur l'appareil exécutant Odoo Point de Vente, "
"contacter votre partenaire d'intégration, car le processus dépend du système "
"d'exploitation de l'appareil."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:80
msgid "Connection over HTTP"
msgstr "Connexion via HTTP"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:82
msgid ""
"To connect the Cashmatic machine over HTTP, use one of the following methods:"
msgstr ""
"Pour connecter la machine Cashmatic via HTTP, utiliser l'une des méthodes "
"suivantes :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:84
msgid ""
"On the Cashmatic machine, log in, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Trusted "
"mode`, then click :guilabel:`Yes`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la machine Cashmatic, se connecter, aller à "
":menuselection:`Paramètres --> Mode de confiance`, puis cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Oui`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:86
msgid ""
"In the MyCashmatic app or on the website, sign in to your account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> System`, then enable :guilabel:`Unsecured "
"APIs`."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'application MyCashmatic ou sur le site web, se connecter à votre "
"compte, aller à :menuselection:`Paramètres --> Système`, puis activer "
":guilabel:`APIs non sécurisées`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:90
msgid ""
"`Cashmatic user manual <https://cashmatic.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/"
"EN-6.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Manuel utilisateur Cashmatic <https://cashmatic.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/"
"02/EN-6.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:97
msgid "To connect the Cashmatic machine to Odoo, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour connecter la machine Cashmatic à Odoo, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:99
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`POS Cashmatic Cash Machines` "
"(`pos_cashmatic`) module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installer <general/install>` le module :guilabel:`POS Cashmatic Cash "
"Machines` (`pos_cashmatic`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:105
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Integration` field to :guilabel:`Cash Machine "
"(Cashmatic)`."
msgstr ""
"Définir le champ :guilabel:`Intégration` sur :guilabel:`Caisse automatique "
"(Cashmatic)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:106
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Cashmatic Settings` tab, enter the Cashmatic "
"machine's :ref:`IP address <pos/cashmatic/ip-address>` in "
"the :guilabel:`Cashmatic IP` field."
msgstr ""
"Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Paramètres Cashmatic`, saisir l':ref:`adresse IP "
"<pos/cashmatic/ip-address>` de la machine Cashmatic dans le champ "
":guilabel:`IP Cashmatic`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:108
msgid ""
"Enter the provided Cashmatic credentials in the :guilabel:`Cashmatic "
"Username` and :guilabel:`Cashmatic Password` fields."
msgstr ""
"Saisir les identifiants Cashmatic fournis dans les champs :guilabel:`Nom "
"d'utilisateur Cashmatic` et :guilabel:`Mot de passe Cashmatic`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashmatic.rst:110
msgid ""
"Optionally, enable :guilabel:`Cashmatic Local Network Access` to connect the "
"machine over `HTTP`."
msgstr ""
"En option, activer :guilabel:`Accès réseau local Cashmatic` pour connecter "
"la machine via `HTTP`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:3
msgid "Glory"
msgstr "Glory"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Glory <https://www.glory-global.com/en-us>`_ :doc:`cash machines <../"
"cash_machines>` enable the automation of cash transactions."
msgstr ""
"Les :doc:`caisses automatiques <../cash_machines>` `Glory <https://www.glory-"
"global.com/en-us>`_ permettent l'automatisation des transactions en espèces."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:9
msgid "Odoo supports the Glory CI-5, CI-10, and CI-10X models."
msgstr "Odoo prend en charge les modèles Glory CI-5, CI-10 et CI-10X."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:10
msgid ""
"The Glory machine must run firmware version ISP-K05H/B v18.40 or later. Any "
"version starting with ISP-K35 is **not supported**."
msgstr ""
"La machine Glory doit exécuter la version de firmware ISP-K05H/B v18.40 ou "
"ultérieure. Toute version commençant par ISP-K35 n'est **pas prise en "
"charge**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:13
msgid ""
"The integration with the Glory cash machine only supports basic functions, "
"such as cash transactions and cash count checks."
msgstr ""
"L'intégration avec la caisse automatique Glory ne prend en charge que les "
"fonctions de base, telles que les transactions en espèces et les "
"vérifications de comptage d'espèces."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:24
msgid "Cash machine settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de la machine à espèces"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:26
msgid ""
"Power on the cash machine, which briefly displays its IP address at the "
"bottom of the screen. Note it down for later."
msgstr ""
"Allumer la machine à espèces, qui affiche brièvement son adresse IP en bas "
"de l'écran. La noter pour plus tard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:30
msgid ""
"The IP address should be formatted as `###.###.#.##` (e.g., `192.168.0.25`)."
msgstr ""
"L'adresse IP doit être formatée comme `###.###.#.##` (par exemple, "
"`192.168.0.25`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:32
msgid ""
"Navigate to the cash machine's homepage by entering its IP address as the "
"URL in `HTTPS` (e.g., `https://192.168.0.25`), and log in with your Glory "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Accéder à la page d'accueil de la machine à espèces en saisissant son "
"adresse IP comme URL en `HTTPS` (par exemple, `https://192.168.0.25`), et se "
"connecter avec vos identifiants Glory."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:34
msgid ""
"As long as the certificate is not imported, a warning page appears when "
"trying to access the machine's homepage. Bypass it by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Advanced` and then :guilabel:`Proceed to [IP address] "
"(unsafe)`."
msgstr ""
"Tant que le certificat n'est pas importé, une page d'avertissement apparaît "
"lors de la tentative d'accès à la page d'accueil de la machine. La "
"contourner en cliquant sur :guilabel:`Avancé` puis sur :guilabel:`Continuer "
"vers [adresse IP] (non sécurisé)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:37
msgid ""
"From the Glory homepage, go to :guilabel:`Host Configuration` and ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Network` setting is set to :guilabel:`MANUAL`, meaning the IP "
"address is static."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la page d'accueil Glory, aller dans :guilabel:`Configuration hôte` et "
"s'assurer que le paramètre :guilabel:`Réseau` est défini "
"sur :guilabel:`MANUEL`, ce qui signifie que l'adresse IP est statique."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:39
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :guilabel:`SSL Configuration` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` section."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, accéder à :guilabel:`Configuration SSL` et faire défiler jusqu'à la "
"section :guilabel:`Paramètre serveur HTTPS`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:42
msgid ""
"In parallel, open the terminal and verify that *OpenSSL* is installed. Type "
"`openssl` and press enter. If installed, this command displays a `help` menu "
"listing all available OpenSSL commands. If nothing happens, `install it "
"<https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."
msgstr ""
"En parallèle, ouvrir le terminal et vérifier que *OpenSSL* est installé. "
"Taper `openssl` et appuyer sur Entrée. Si installé, cette commande affiche "
"un menu `help` répertoriant toutes les commandes OpenSSL disponibles. Si "
"rien ne se passe, `l'installer <https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:45
msgid ""
"Then, paste the following command and press `Enter` to generate and download "
"the certificate and private key. Ensure that you replace the demo IP address "
"with the cash machine’s actual IP address."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, coller la commande suivante et appuyer sur `Entrée` pour générer et "
"télécharger le certificat et la clé privée. S'assurer de remplacer l'adresse "
"IP de démonstration par l'adresse IP réelle de la machine à espèces."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:54
msgid ""
"The self-signed SSL certificate and key pair must use the same static IP "
"address as the cash machine."
msgstr ""
"Le certificat SSL auto-signé et la paire de clés doivent utiliser la même "
"adresse IP statique que la machine à espèces."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:57
msgid ""
"Once the files are generated, from the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` "
"section, upload `cert.pem` as the :guilabel:`Certificate` and `key.pem` as "
"the :guilabel:`Private Key`."
msgstr ""
"Une fois les fichiers générés, depuis la section :guilabel:`Paramètre "
"serveur HTTPS`, téléverser `cert.pem` comme :guilabel:`Certificat` et "
"`key.pem` comme :guilabel:`Clé privée`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:59
msgid ""
"Go to :guilabel:`WebApp Configuration` and ensure the :guilabel:`Interface` "
"setting from the :guilabel:`A: Nodejs Setting` section is set "
"to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Aller dans :guilabel:`Configuration WebApp` et s'assurer que le "
"paramètre :guilabel:`Interface` de la section :guilabel:`A: Paramètre "
"Nodejs` est défini sur :guilabel:`Activer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:61
msgid "Then, adjust the following settings depending on the POS setup:"
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, ajuster les paramètres suivants en fonction de la configuration du "
"Point de Vente :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:63
msgid ""
"If **multiple POS** are connected to the same cash machine, go "
"to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`SOAP IF "
"Setting`, and ensure :guilabel:`Session mode` and :guilabel:`Occupy mode` "
"are both set to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Si **plusieurs Point de Vente** sont connectés à la même machine à espèces, "
"aller dans :guilabel:`Configuration App`, faire défiler "
"jusqu'à :guilabel:`Paramètre SOAP IF`, et s'assurer que :guilabel:`Mode "
"session` et :guilabel:`Mode occupation` sont tous deux définis "
"sur :guilabel:`Activer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:66
msgid ""
"If **a dedicated user** has been set up on the cash machine for Odoo, which "
"is recommended, go to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`SOAP IF Setting` section, and :guilabel:`Enable` "
"the :guilabel:`User check` setting."
msgstr ""
"Si **un utilisateur dédié** a été configuré sur la machine de caisse pour "
"Odoo, ce qui est recommandé, aller dans :guilabel:`Configuration de "
"l'application`, descendre jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Paramètre SOAP IF`, "
"et :guilabel:`Activer` le paramètre :guilabel:`Vérification utilisateur`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:69
msgid "Restart the cash machine to apply the new settings."
msgstr ""
"Redémarrer la machine à espèces pour appliquer les nouveaux paramètres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:72
msgid ""
"As this setup is complex and may involve advanced knowledge of Glory "
"hardware, it is advisable to consult the Glory integration partner for "
"configuration if there is any uncertainty."
msgstr ""
"Cette configuration étant complexe et pouvant nécessiter des connaissances "
"avancées du matériel Glory, il est conseillé de consulter le partenaire "
"d'intégration Glory pour la configuration en cas de doute."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:76
msgid "Import self-signed certificates"
msgstr "Importer les certificats auto-signés"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:78
