#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/dpo.rst:3
msgid "DPO Pay"
msgstr "DPO Pay"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/dpo.rst:5
msgid ""
"`DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/>`_ offers in-store payment solutions for "
"customer transactions through several physical `terminals <https://"
"dpogroup.com/products/network-pos/>`_. These terminals support swiping, "
"scanning, or tapping credit and debit cards (Visa, MasterCard, and American "
"Express), as well as Mobile payments (Airtel Money and M-Pesa)."
msgstr ""
"`DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/>`_ propose des solutions de paiement en "
"magasin pour les transactions clients via plusieurs `terminaux <https://"
"dpogroup.com/products/network-pos/>`_ physiques. Ces terminaux prennent en "
"charge le glissement, le scan ou le contact de cartes de crédit et de débit "
"(Visa, MasterCard et American Express), ainsi que les paiements mobiles "
"(Airtel Money et M-Pesa)."

