#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:3
msgid "Ingenico"
msgstr "Ingenico"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/stripe.rst:5
msgid ""
"Connecting a payment terminal allows you to offer a fluid payment flow to "
"your customers and ease the work of your cashiers."
msgstr ""
"La connexion d'un terminal de paiement vous permet d'offrir un flux de "
"paiement fluide à vos clients et facilite le travail de vos caissiers."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:9
msgid ""
"Ingenico payment terminals require an :doc:`IoT system </applications/"
"general/iot>`."
msgstr ""
"Les terminaux de paiement Ingenico nécessitent un :doc:`système IoT </"
"applications/general/iot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:10
msgid ""
"Ingenico is currently only available in Belgium, the Netherlands and "
"Luxembourg."
msgstr ""
"Ingenico n'est actuellement disponible qu'en Belgique, aux Pays-Bas et au "
"Luxembourg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:11
msgid ""
"Odoo works with the Ingenico Lane/, Desk/, and Move/ payment terminals as "
"they support the TLV communication protocol through TCP/IP."
msgstr ""
"Odoo fonctionne avec les terminaux de paiement Ingenico Lane/, Desk/ et "
"Move/ car ils prennent en charge le protocole de communication TLV via TCP/"
"IP."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:18
msgid "Connect an IoT system"
msgstr "Connecter un système IoT"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:20
msgid ""
"Connecting an Ingenico payment terminal to Odoo is a feature that requires "
"an IoT system. For more information on how to connect an IoT system to your "
"database, please refer to the :doc:`IoT documentation </applications/general/"
"iot>`."
msgstr ""
"La connexion d'un terminal de paiement Ingenico à Odoo est une "
"fonctionnalité qui nécessite un système IoT. Pour plus d'informations sur la "
"connexion d'un système IoT à votre base de données, veuillez consulter "
"la :doc:`documentation IoT </applications/general/iot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:25
msgid "Configure the Lane/Desk/Move 5000 terminals for Ingenico BENELUX"
msgstr "Configurer les terminaux Lane/Desk/Move 5000 pour Ingenico BENELUX"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:27
msgid ""
"Press the function button (:guilabel:`F` on Lane/5000, :guilabel:`⦿` on Desk/"
"5000 and Move/5000)."
msgstr ""
"Appuyer sur le bouton fonction (:guilabel:`F` sur Lane/5000, :guilabel:`⦿` "
"sur Desk/5000 et Move/5000)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:29
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Kassa menu --> Settings Menu` and enter the settings "
"password (default: `2009`)."
msgstr ""
"Aller dans :menuselection:`Kassa menu --> Settings Menu` et saisir le mot de "
"passe des paramètres (par défaut : `2009`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:31
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Change Connection` and press :guilabel:`OK` on the next "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner :guilabel:`Change Connection` et appuyer sur :guilabel:`OK` à "
"l'écran suivant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:32
msgid "Select :guilabel:`TCP/IP` and :guilabel:`IP-address`."
msgstr "Sélectionner :guilabel:`TCP/IP` et :guilabel:`IP-address`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:33
msgid "On the next screen, enter the IP address of your IoT system."
msgstr "À l'écran suivant, saisir l'adresse IP de votre système IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:34
msgid ""
"Enter `9000` as port number and press :guilabel:`OK` on the next screen."
msgstr ""
"Saisir `9000` comme numéro de port et appuyer sur :guilabel:`OK` à l'écran "
"suivant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:36
msgid ""
"At this point, the terminal restarts and should be displayed on the IoT "
"system's form in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"À ce stade, le terminal redémarre et devrait s'afficher sur le formulaire du "
"système IoT dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:44
msgid ""
"Enable the payment terminal :ref:`in the application settings <pos/use/"
"settings>` and :doc:`create the related payment method <../../"
"payment_methods>`. Set the journal type as :guilabel:`Bank` and "
"select :guilabel:`Ingenico` in the :guilabel:`Use a Payment Terminal` field. "
"Then, select your terminal device in the :guilabel:`Payment Terminal Device` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Activer le terminal de paiement :ref:`dans les paramètres de l'application "
"<pos/use/settings>` et :doc:`créer le mode de paiement associé <../../"
"payment_methods>`. Définir le type de journal comme :guilabel:`Banque` et "
"sélectionner :guilabel:`Ingenico` dans le champ :guilabel:`Utiliser un "
"terminal de paiement`. Ensuite, sélectionner votre terminal dans le "
"champ :guilabel:`Terminal de paiement`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/ingenico.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once the payment method is created, you can select it in your POS settings. "
"To do so, go to the :ref:`POS' settings <pos/use/settings>`, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`, and add the payment method under "
"the :guilabel:`Payments` section."
msgstr ""
"Une fois la méthode de paiement créée, vous pouvez la sélectionner dans les "
"paramètres de votre Point de Vente. Pour cela, aller dans "
"les :ref:`paramètres du Point de Vente <pos/use/settings>`, cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Modifier`, et ajouter la méthode de paiement dans la "
"section :guilabel:`Paiements`."

