#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:139
msgid "Invoice generation via QR code and URL"
msgstr "Génération de factures via code QR et URL"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:141
msgid ""
"To allow customers to request an invoice by scanning a QR code printed on "
"their :ref:`receipt <pos/configuration/receipts>`, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pour permettre aux clients de demander une facture en scannant un code QR "
"imprimé sur leur :ref:`reçu <pos/configuration/receipts>`, suivre ces "
"étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:145
msgid "Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Bills & Receipts` section."
msgstr "Faire défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Factures et reçus`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:146
msgid "Enable the :guilabel:`Self-service invoicing` setting."
msgstr "Activer le paramètre :guilabel:`Facturation en libre-service`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:147
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Print` field to :guilabel:`QR code`, :guilabel:`URL`, "
"or :guilabel:`QR code + URL` to determine how customers can access their "
"invoice (e.g., by scanning the QR code or by typing the URL in a browser)."
msgstr ""
"Définir le champ :guilabel:`Imprimer` sur :guilabel:`Code "
"QR`, :guilabel:`URL` ou :guilabel:`Code QR + URL` pour déterminer comment "
"les clients peuvent accéder à leur facture (par exemple, en scannant le code "
"QR ou en saisissant l'URL dans un navigateur)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:151
msgid ""
"Upon scanning the QR code or typing the URL in a browser, customers must "
"fill in a form with the information on the receipt (i.e., "
"the :guilabel:`Ticket Number`, :guilabel:`Date`, and :guilabel:`Unique "
"code`) and click :guilabel:`Request Invoice`. Then, they must enter their "
"billing information or sign in and click :guilabel:`Get my invoice`. The "
"invoice is then generated and available for download, and the order status "
"is updated to :guilabel:`Fully Invoiced`."
msgstr ""
"Lors du scan du code QR ou de la saisie de l'URL dans un navigateur, les "
"clients doivent remplir un formulaire avec les informations figurant sur le "
"reçu (c'est-à-dire le :guilabel:`Numéro de ticket`, la :guilabel:`Date` et "
"le :guilabel:`Code unique`) et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Demander une facture`. "
"Ensuite, ils doivent saisir leurs informations de facturation ou se "
"connecter et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Obtenir ma facture`. La facture est "
"alors générée et disponible en téléchargement, et le statut de la commande "
"est mis à jour sur :guilabel:`Entièrement facturé`."

