#~ msgid ""
#~ "Win/Loss is a calculation of active or previously active leads in a "
#~ "pipeline that were either marked as **Won** or **Lost** over a specific "
#~ "period of time. By calculating opportunities won over opportunities lost, "
#~ "teams can clarify key performance indicators (KPIs) that are converting "
#~ "leads into sales, such as specific teams or team members, certain "
#~ "marketing mediums or campaigns, and so on."
